-- North Korea Building Tunnel for Possible Nuclear Test, Chosun Ilbo Reports
-- B y   B o m i   L i m
-- 2010-12-14T22:02:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-14/north-korea-building-tunnel-for-possible-nuclear-test-chosun-ilbo-reports.html
North Korea is building a tunnel at
a site where it conducted two underground nuclear tests, the
Chosun Ilbo newspaper reported, citing a South Korean
intelligence official it didn’t identify. North Korea may be
able to conduct a nuclear test as early as March at the rate the
tunnel is being built at Punggyeri in the country’s northeastern
corner, the Korean-language newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bomi Lim in Seoul at 
 blim30@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
